<DocsPageTitle>
    NumericPicker component
</DocsPageTitle>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    Use <Code Tag>NumericPicker</Code> to have a field for any kind of numeric values.
    All basic types are supported, including nullable types
    (<Code>int</Code>, <Code>long</Code>, <Code>float</Code>, <Code>double</Code>, <Code>decimal</Code>, etc.).
</DocsPageParagraph>

